  <h1>Mobile & Internet Setup for Gulf Expats 2026</h1>

  <div class="not-prose mb-6 p-4 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 rounded-lg">
    <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Country-specific telecom guides</p>
